title: CoinGecko’s New Coin Index Now Features ERC-20 Token, Golden Inu ($GOLDEN)
description: In a significant move, CoinGecko, the renowned cryptocurrency platform, has now unveiled the latest addition to its listings – the new ERC-20 Token, Golden Inu (GOLDEN), arriving to the list on Thursday at or around 6 AM Eastern. This listing instantaneously triggered a surge in trading activity for the ‘Dogecoin Killer,’ boasting an impressive uptick [...]
